quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  9,111,DI ACXET believers their viv their MON Paradise. Tiel ili batal ig DI testament kill get killed Such est His truthful pledge Torah Gospel Quran - who fulfills His pledge put than DI? Vi gxoj far such exchange This est greatest triumf
