  9,117,DI redeemed prophet immigrants (Muhajireen) supporters hosted them DON them RIFUGX (Ansar) SEKV him difficult TEMP! Ke est when kor de kelk da them preskaux wavered Li redeemed them Li est Compassionate towards them Merciful
